articles.title: Aave CEO Wants to Tokenize Tesla. Elon Musk Gives Silent Treatment
articles.description: Maybe Musk just hasn’t checked his Twitter mentions?
articles.content:
Aave co-founder and CEO Stani Kulechov really wants Tesla to join the decentralized finance (DeFi) craze.
